metadata.name: SpaceX Ether Astronauts #2
metadata.description: SpaceX Ether Astronauts, is a collection of different Astronauts with a different traits, 2030 is the year, in which most of us will be reaching to Mars, and starting a new life on Mars, as part of earth evacuation Astronauts, Elon Musk and SpaceX will play an important role in evacuating Mankind to the Mars, Fasten your seat belt and be prepared for the Mars ride.
